Package: pllr
Title: Premier Lacrosse League Stats API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Description: R client for the Premier Lacrosse League (PLL) stats API.
    Provides functions to retrieve standings, player stats, events,
    draft information, and free agent data as tibbles.
